name: Elysium Anime
description:
These are out of date models now I think but I have uploaded them here for archive. Differences from the original models: converted to safetensors, fp16, clip fixed and have the kl-f8-anime2 VAE baked in.

These were originally on my huggingface here:

https://huggingface.co/hesw23168

Recommended settings:

  • Negative prompt: (lowres:1.1), (worst quality:1.2), (low quality:1.1), bad anatomy, bad hands, text, error, missing fingers, extra digit, fewer digits, cropped, normal quality, jpeg artifacts, signature, watermark, username, blurry

  • Clip skip 1 or 2, VAE: 'kl-f8-anime2' from Waifu Diffusion (already baked into model)
